ActCanada Wildlife Act
SubjectCap Tourmente National Wildlife Area ** Acquisition of lands **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of the Environment to acquire lands to be added subsequently to the CAP TOURMENTE NATIONAL WILDLIFE AREA, in Quebec for the purpose of research, conservation and interpretation in respect of migratory birds in order to support the Department of the Environment’s commitment to protect Canada’s wildlife and preserve the country’s natural heritage.
